&lt;h2 id="IPython's-Rich-Display-System"&gt;IPython's Rich Display System&lt;a class="anchor-link" href="http://farley.futuresight.io/posts/jupyter-notebook-demo/#IPython's-Rich-Display-System"&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
